穿了内增高没看出来比我矮，后来在一起了才慢慢觉察，直到现在问他到底多高也不说，说怕我在意。 现在真的不知道该怎么办好了，我们家庭条件都一般，他对我确实很包容，我们相处起来也比较轻松吧，我很看重这点，但是身高让我特别在意，现在也没有一点喜欢了，就是习惯和依赖。但谈到结婚，真的不想结。一眼看到头的生活，提不起爱意的对象，让我没有一点结婚的勇气，但说分手总觉得有些舍不得，也怕伤了他。如果跟他结婚就是为了结婚而结婚。实在不知道怎么办才好了"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/514831617"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I26y18bOIg9JEEAMaCDc2Njg4NDE1IIrx9o8GMDI45wtALnIJNTE0ODMxNjE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1644120260.3666015", "card_id": "Q_469750082", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 136}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "开车回家过年，为什么有人开 800 公里没事，有人 200 公里就累倒？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-25c034b27edb526f45a2738e91134388_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/469750082"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I26y18bOIg9JEEAMaCDY2NjY4NzMzINqAgIcGMAM4twNAL3IJNDY5NzUwMDgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1644120260.3669102", "card_id": "Q_513853043", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 42}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些充满爱意的温柔句子？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-11baa0b6930883eda3d1d539446c8d19_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/513853043"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I26y18bOIg9JEEAMaCDc2NDcxMTEyIKTBz48GMAA4pQFAMHIJNTEzODUzMDQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1644120260.3672066", "card_id": "Q_514369368", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 200}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "学历